data.description:
Well maintained home in the Montford district with 4 bedrooms, full bath an a half-bath. The First impression of the home is the large front porch with a Swing. Walking in on main level, living room with a non usable fireplace, Bedroom with a non-usable fire place, Dining room with a non-usable Fire place, Half bath and Kitchen with a back porch that leads to the back yard  storage shed and access to driveway  with 4-5 parking spaces.  The second floor has 3 bedrooms and full bath. there are Non-useable fireplaces in 2 of the bedrooms. All bedrooms and bath can be accessed from the  spacious hall. Furance in place for each floor.
walkable neighborhood to downtown Asheville and Harrah Center, less than five minutes from Merrimon Ave. with bank, grocery stores restaurants and much more, less than Five minutes to interstate 240 and hwy 19/23.

from 240 take the Montford exit. stay on Montford, turn right on West Chestnut, turn left on Flint Street, blue house on left.
